    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两位小小朋友，在一个吓人的世界中迷失了──那是个对小孩不友善的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们必须设法逃离“虚无之地”，否则会面对比死亡更悲惨的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・一起面对童年阴影</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将化为小洛与小寂，他们在这个令人感到寂寞的梦魇中相遇，从那之后一直是最好的朋友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小洛与小寂拿着各自的代表性道具──弓箭以及扳手。他们一起潜行，穿过隐藏通道，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >互相拉起彼此、跨越重重障碍，观察彼此身后有无危险，合作无间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能够和好友或是AI同伴，靠着彼此的代表性道具创造机会、向前迈进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四周的环境中藏有许多线索与可能性，让孩子发挥想象力与多方探索──</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小洛的弓箭可以射中较高的目标、射断绳索，或是射下空中的敌人；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小寂的扳手能敲晕敌人、打坏障碍物，或是用来操作各种机械。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392860/extras/16021adf66230203ec6533eccdb3870f.poster.avif?t=1767887616\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392860/extras/16021adf66230203ec6533eccdb3870f.webm?t=1767887616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・跃入沉浸感十足 却也胆颤心惊的冒险</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论走到哪里，整个“虚无之地”都是恐怖怪物的巢穴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里的居民一发现不请自来的小小访客，肯定会千里迢迢跑来抓人──</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在墓城的沙漠遗迹遇到巨婴宝宝，一场恐怖版的鬼抓人游戏即将展开；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进糖果工厂的时候，要躲开一群群贪婪的糖果象鼻虫来袭；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿梭在浸满雨水的游乐场步道时，也要注意闪避大脚的步伐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了能全身而退，你必须随时做好逃跑、躲藏的准备，也要在短时间内集中注意力，挺身保护自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392860/extras/6e739f1d1c409d003e415963f254e75c.poster.avif?t=1767887616\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392860/extras/6e739f1d1c409d003e415963f254e75c.webm?t=1767887616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・深入“漩涡”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“虚无之地”的荒废之美映入眼帘时，请别因此感到却步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不少黑暗的秘密隐藏其中，等着小洛与小寂横越“漩涡”时逐渐揭开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每当他们走到新区域时，危险度与困难度将更胜以往，过去的创伤会浮现眼前──</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小洛与小寂能不能逃离这无穷无尽的梦魇？只有你能帮助这两位小小朋友……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392860/extras/5441df5cb2e53e01e7a4abe2bbeadcf9.poster.avif?t=1767887616\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392860/extras/5441df5cb2e53e01e7a4abe2bbeadcf9.webm?t=1767887616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
